(Republished)

St. Regis Paper Company, Appellant, v. John L. Rayward, Doing Business as Rayward Associates, et al., Respondents.

Order entered on April 6, 1961 unanimously modified, on the law and on the facts, to the extent of dismissing the counterclaim, and, as so modified, affirmed, with $20 costs and disbursements to the appellant. The order of this court entered on March 27, 1962 is vacated. Concur — Botein, P. J., Breitel, Rabin, McNally and Stevens, JJ.
